  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<p>Scheduled for 2/1/2021 at 11:30 CT</p><h3 id=\"id-1.17.16-ImprovementsandBugFixes\">Improvements and Bug Fixes</h3><ul><li><p>Inventory Details List View - You can now add the columns \u201cSerial Number\u201d, \u201cPrice\u201d, \u201cCost\u201d, and \u201cAverage Cost\u201d to the Inventory Details List View. These columns display the serial number (if any), price, cost, and average cost of the inventory item at your location. Note: The \u201cPrice\u201d and \u201cCost\u201d columns may display different values than the \u201cPrice | Cost\u201d column, which displays an item\u2019s <em>catalog</em> price, not the price of the actual <em>inventory</em> item which may have location overrides applied.</p></li><li><p>We fixed a bug where adding, editing, or removing a supplier SKUs from a catalog item did not display the update in the change log at all.</p></li><li><p>We fixed a bug where sometimes users would experience an error when trying to send a ticket approval email to a customer.</p></li></ul>",
